text: Wang Xueyi (Chinese: 王雪毅; born 3 August 1991) is a Chinese high jumper. She won a silver medal at the 2017 Asian Championships and placed fourth at the 2018 Asian Games. ==References== Category:Chinese female long jumpers Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for China
